&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for the role of Deputy Director of Nursing for Medicine Admitted Care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is a supportive role to the Group Director of Nursing and the successful candidate will have their own portfolio to focus upon. Medicine and Emergency Care is a fast paced and dynamic specialty which requires energy, motivation and drive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You would be working within a cohesive team of Matrons and Service Managers and the triumvirate management team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will have previous experience in an acute environment at a senior nursing level of 8a or above.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All enquires please contact Group Director of Nursing Julie Thompson on 07971 382261&lt;/p&gt;
